      • getValueClass

        public Class<?> getValueClass()
        Gets the Class object for the property value. The following algorithm is used: if value is not null, value.getClass will be returned. Otherwise we use information from PropertyDescriptor or BeanDescriptor.

        PropertyDescriptor.getPropertyType(), BeanDescriptor.getBeanClass()
